---
title: Honey-Lemon Turkey with Thyme Roasted Carrots
description: You'll want to keep this honey-lemon pan sauce in your collection – it's so simple but packs in flavour and fragrance! The roasted carrots add a touch of sweetness to the dish and crispy shallots sprinkled over the cream cheese mashed potatoes takes this baby home!
